data.description: Welcome to your new home! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath home offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and serene surroundings. Perfect corner lot with lots of beautiful mature trees. Step inside this beautiful remodeled home and be greeted by an inviting open floorplan, connecting the  living, dining, and kitchen areas. It doesn't stop there. Escape to the outdoors and unwind in the covered patio, where you can enjoy the tranquil views of your own backyard oasis. Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity-schedule your showing today!
